verbose_text: Treatment with JIB-04 4 hr prior to IR exposure robustly increased the intrinsic radiosensitivity of these radioresistant cell lines (XREF_FIG) and markedly decreased the surviving fraction at 2 Gy radiation (SF2) (XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY).
